'''Caburinta ka dhanka ah [[Markhaatiyaasha Yehowah]] ee Poland sanadihii 1945–1956''' - xarig iyo caburin ay Wasaaradda Amniga Dadweynaha ka codsatay Markhaatiyaasha Yehowah ee [[Boland|Poland]]. Ujeeddada ficilku waxay ahayd in la baabi'iyo kooxdan diimeed ee Poland maamulada shuuciga ah. Mowjadda ugu weyn ee qabqabashadu waxay dhacday habeenka Juun 21-22, 1950. Guud ahaan, qiyaastii 5,000 oo qof ayaa la xiray. Marka loo eego tirakoobka dowladda, caburinta muddadan waxay ahayd inay saameyso 90% Markhaatiyaasha Yehowah.

Tan iyo 1989, Markhaatiyaasha Yehowah dr [[Boland]] waxay haysteen xorriyad, 130,000 xubnood.

